member.example:
This sample shows how to call GenEndPointAsync with required parameters.

var endpoint = new Uri("<https://my-service.azure.com>");
var client = new EndpointClient(endpoint);

Response response = await client.GenEndPointAsync("<action>");
Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

This sample shows how to call GenEndPoint with required parameters.

var endpoint = new Uri("<https://my-service.azure.com>");
var client = new EndpointClient(endpoint);

Response response = client.GenEndPoint("<action>");
Console.WriteLine(response.Status);
